data.text:
David Austin Grose

David Austin Grose is an employee with Shasta Ventures, a venture capital company. David is Chief Financial Officer, Shasta Ventures Management, Llc and has served as Chief Financial Officer, Shasta Ventures Management, Llc since 12/01/2004. David Grose has an ownership stake in Shasta Ventures of less than 5%.
